# Intelligence Émotionnelle

^une définition // {"headword":"définition","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
~? Définition de l'**intelligence émotionnelle** :
^une capacité // {"headword":"capacité","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^percevoir // {"headword":"percevoir","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^comprendre // {"headword":"comprendre","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^gérer // {"headword":"gérer","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^exprimer // {"headword":"exprimer","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^une émotion // {"headword":"émotion","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
-**capacité** à **percevoir**, **comprendre**, **gérer** et **exprimer** ses **émotions**,
-ainsi que **celles des autres**
^résoudre // {"headword":"résoudre","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^un problème // {"headword":"problème","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^réguler // {"headword":"réguler","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^un comportement // {"headword":"comportement","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
-pour **résoudre** les **problèmes** et **réguler** les **comportements**

^une empathie // {"headword":"empathie","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
~? Définition de l'**empathie** :
^adopter // {"headword":"adopter","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^une perspective // {"headword":"perspective","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
-**capacité** à **adopter** la **perspective** de l'**autre**
^un ressenti // {"headword":"ressenti","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
-pour **percevoir** et **comprendre** **son ressenti**.

^the intelligence // {"headword":"intelligence","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^emotional // {"headword":"emotional","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^the emotional intelligence // {"headword":"emotional intelligence","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"C1"}
# Emotional Intelligence

^the definition // {"headword":"definition","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
~?Definition of **emotional intelligence**:
^the ability // {"headword":"ability","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^perceive // {"headword":"perceive","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"C1"}
^understand // {"headword":"understand","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^manage // {"headword":"manage","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^express // {"headword":"express","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^the emotion // {"headword":"emotion","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
-**ability** to **perceive**, **understand**, **manage** and **express** one's **emotions**,
-as well as **those of others**
^solve // {"headword":"solve","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^the problem // {"headword":"problem","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^regulate // {"headword":"regulate","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"C1"}
^the behavior // {"headword":"behavior","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
-to **solve problems** and **regulate behaviors**

^the empathy // {"headword":"empathy","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"C1"}
~?Definition of **empathy**:
^adopt // {"headword":"adopt","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^the perspective // {"headword":"perspective","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
-**ability** to **adopt the other person's perspective**
^the feelings // {"headword":"feelings","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A2"}
-to **perceive** and **understand** **their feelings**.

^die Intelligenz // {"headword":"Intelligenz","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^emotional // {"headword":"emotional","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^die emotionale Intelligenz // {"headword":"emotionale Intelligenz","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"C1"}
# Emotionale Intelligenz

^die Definition // {"headword":"Definition","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
~?Definition der **emotionalen** **Intelligenz**:
^die Fähigkeit // {"headword":"Fähigkeit","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^wahrnehmen // {"headword":"wahrnehmen","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^verstehen // {"headword":"verstehen","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^handhaben // {"headword":"handhaben","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^ausdrücken // {"headword":"ausdrücken","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^die Emotion // {"headword":"Emotion","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
-**Fähigkeit**, die eigenen **Emotionen** zu **wahrnehmen**, **verstehen**, **handhaben** und **ausdrücken**,
-sowie **die der anderen**
^lösen // {"headword":"lösen","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^das Problem // {"headword":"Problem","category":"noun","gender":"neuter","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^regulieren // {"headword":"regulieren","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^die Verhaltensweise // {"headword":"Verhaltensweise","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
-um **Probleme zu lösen** und **Verhaltensweisen zu regulieren**

^die Empathie // {"headword":"Empathie","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
~?Definition der **Empathie**:
^einnehmen // {"headword":"einnehmen","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^die Perspektive // {"headword":"Perspektive","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
-**Fähigkeit**, **die Perspektive des anderen einzunehmen**
^das Empfinden // {"headword":"Empfinden","category":"noun","gender":"neuter","cefrLevel":"C1"}
-um **sein Empfinden** zu **wahrnehmen** und **verstehen**.

^智力 // {"headword":"智力","category":"noun","pinyin":"zhì lì","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^一种情绪 // {"headword":"情绪","category":"noun","pinyin":"qíng xù","cefrLevel":"B1","classifier":"种"}
