# 情绪智力

^一个定义 // {"headword":"定义","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"dìng yì","cefrLevel":"B2"}
~?情绪智力的定义：
^一种能力 // {"headword":"能力","category":"noun","classifier":"种","pinyin":"néng lì","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^感知 // {"headword":"感知","category":"verb","pinyin":"gǎn zhī","cefrLevel":"C1"}
^理解 // {"headword":"理解","category":"verb","pinyin":"lǐ jiě","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^管理 // {"headword":"管理","category":"verb","pinyin":"guǎn lǐ","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^表达 // {"headword":"表达","category":"verb","pinyin":"biǎo dá","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^一种情绪 // {"headword":"情绪","category":"noun","classifier":"种","pinyin":"qíng xù","cefrLevel":"B1"}
-**能力**去**感知**、**理解**、**管理**和**表达**自己的**情绪**，
-以及**他人的情绪**
^解决 // {"headword":"解决","category":"verb","pinyin":"jiě jué","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^一个问题 // {"headword":"问题","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"wèn tí","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^调节 // {"headword":"调节","category":"verb","pinyin":"tiáo jié","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^一种行为 // {"headword":"行为","category":"noun","classifier":"种","pinyin":"xíng wéi","cefrLevel":"B2"}
-以便**解决问题**和**调节行为**

^一种共情 // {"headword":"共情","category":"noun","classifier":"种","pinyin":"gòng qíng","cefrLevel":"C1"}
~?共情的定义：
^采纳 // {"headword":"采纳","category":"verb","pinyin":"cǎi nà","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^一个视角 // {"headword":"视角","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"shì jiǎo","cefrLevel":"B2"}
-**能力**去**采纳他人的视角**
^一种感受 // {"headword":"感受","category":"noun","classifier":"种","pinyin":"gǎn shòu","cefrLevel":"B1"}
-以便**感知**和**理解****他人的感受**。
